        "text": "Yeah, I think that's a great one. Here we go. \"I wish to preach not the doctrine of ignoble ease, but the doctrine of the strenuous life.\" The strenuous life. That's what it is. And to me, that's just giving your all to everything that you do.",
        "speaker": "Sander Schulhoff"
