      "And the reality is, don't do that.",
      "So you need to be great at product strategy to be a product leader, you need to be great at growth strategy to be a growth leader.",
      "So I think the key there is smart and driven people for sure.",
      "So if you're going to hire a junior person, the key is, how do you help them learn? And I think if you don't know what you're doing as the founder or the leader, it's hard."
